title: 07- Anxiety vs. Trust
description:
So many of us are living afraid. Let’s talk about it and what Scripture says about our spiraling anxiety. God has given us a way out of our crippling fear.

To take this a step further today, go to https://www.jennieallen.com/anxiousthoughtsguide to download the FREE Anxious Thoughts Guide.

Read Get Out of Your Head book with friends and use the free GOOYH book club kit here: jennieallen.com

We love the Dwell app and made a special audio Scripture plan to help you stop spiraling toxic thoughts: https://dwellapp.io/jennie
